text:
Asahi, she's not here yet.
It's been 20 minutes already...
And there's been no contact either...

Oh! Asahi!
I was worried because you were late.

Haha. I was mixed up with some interesting
performers I met.

...!?
Um, what do you mean by that?
Anyway, we need to go soon, right?
Oh, Producer-san, there's a dog I've never seen before!
I'm going to check it out~!

No, no, Asahi...!
I understand how you feel, but we're running out of time...!
